member.name: AUDIT_EVENT_TYPE
member.summary: The AUDIT_EVENT_TYPE enumeration type defines values that indicate the type of object being audited. The and functions use these values.

member.name: AUDIT_EVENT_TYPE.AuditEventObjectAccess
member.summary: Indicates an object that generates audit messages only if the system administrator has enabled auditing access to files and objects.

member.name: AUDIT_EVENT_TYPE.AuditEventDirectoryServiceAccess
member.summary: Indicates a directory service object that generates audit messages only if the system administrator has enabled auditing access to directory service objects.
